10) UI contract (XL)
Form: monthly investment, horizon, target CAGR, risk slider, sector caps.

Results view: allocations table (+ CSV download), KPI cards (exp CAGR, vol, DD), charts (weights by sector, efficient frontier optional), and an explanation panel (from explain.py).

Shareable permalink: /portfolio/{run_id} resolves via IL.

11) Governance & audit
Run registry: every optimization persists params_json, constraints, model_tag, code_version, data_version.

Model cards: short markdown describing objective, constraints, assumptions, limitations.

Kill-switch: feature flag to disable new runs if data quality checks fail.

